sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo Workflows
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Steps as Pipeline Step Pods
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Storage (MinIO)<br/>9000/TCP S3 API

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(RBAC check)
    Proxy->>API: Forward request<br/>HTTP(S) PodToPodTLS

    API->>DB: Store pipeline definition<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: Password
    DB-->>API: OK

    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>S3 API 9000/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>API: OK

    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>API: Workflow created

    API-->>Route: Pipeline run started
    Route-->>User: 200 OK

    Note over WFC,Steps: Workflow Execution

    WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow event

    WFC->>K8s: Create step pods<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    K8s-->>WFC: Pods created

    Steps->>MLMD: Log metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy
    MLMD-->>Steps: OK

    Steps->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>S3 API 9000/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>Steps: OK

    Note over PA,MLMD: Artifact Persistence

    PA->>API: Fetch run status<br/>HTTP(S) 8888/TCP<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    API-->>PA: Run artifacts

    PA->>MLMD: Sync metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD-->>PA: OK

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Managed Pipeline Import

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
        participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        DSPO->>OCI: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Default keychain
        OCI-->>DSPO: OCI image layers

        Note over DSPO: Cache by digest (10min TTL)<br/>Extract from newest layer

        DSPO->>K8s: Create API Server with<br/>init container + shared volume
        Note over API: Init container pre-loads<br/>pipeline definitions
        API->>DB: Import pipeline definitions<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP
    end

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        DSPO->>K8s: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>CRUD child resources<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        DSPO->>DB: Health check<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>Auth: Password
        DB-->>DSPO: OK
        DSPO->>S3: Health check<br/>S3 API 9000/TCP<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
        S3-->>DSPO: OK
    end
